Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,女人送了个眼色过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,八五郎也也扯足了嗓子喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,音羽屋 音羽屋 音羽屋 音羽屋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.55,0:23:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,音羽音羽音羽音羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,音羽屋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.58,zs,,0,0,0,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}注：
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.58,zsx,,0,0,0,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(1500,0,1,\fscx0)}———————
